OL,3,CPolice deploy drone cameras in hunt
OL,4,Cfor those who fired objects at drivers
OL,6,FPolice drones with thermal imaging
OL,7,Fcameras are being flown near two major
OL,8,Froads in Kent to help deter, and find
OL,9,Fthose responsible for firing objects
OL,10,Fat vehicles.
OL,12,FDrivers who have been targeted on the
OL,13,FA2 near Darenth and on the M20 near
OL,14,FSnodland, have had their vehicles
OL,15,Fdamaged.
OL,17,FKent Police have also launched patrols
OL,18,Fincluding unmarked vehicles following
OL,19,Freported incidents on the evening of
OL,20,FThursday 7 November 2024.
