OL,3,CPolice deploy drone cameras in hunt
OL,4,Cfor those who fired objects at drivers
OL,6,FThe incident on the A2 involved
OL,7,Fobjects being fired from an area
OL,8,Fadjacent to the carriageway at around
OL,9,F5.50pm, causing the windows and
OL,10,Fbodywork on several vehicles to be
OL,11,Fdamaged.
OL,13,FBut officers say they are not linking
OL,14,Fthose reports to others received
OL,15,Fbetween 9pm and 10pm on the M20, where
OL,16,Fa number of drivers reported their
OL,17,Fvehicles being struck by items that
OL,18,Fhad possibly fallen from a nearby
OL,19,Fbridge.
