OL,3,CPolice deploy drone cameras in hunt
OL,4,Cfor those who fired objects at drivers
OL,6,FChief Inspector Craig West of Kent
OL,7,FPolice said: "Throwing or firing items
OL,8,Fat moving traffic is incredibly
OL,9,Fdangerous and it is fortunate nobody
OL,10,Fwas injured as a result of either of
OL,11,Fthese incidents.
OL,13,F"Anyone found to have been responsible
OL,14,Ffor putting road users in danger can
OL,15,Fexpect to be arrested and brought
OL,16,Fbefore the courts.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
