OL,4,Cfor those who fired objects at drivers
OL,6,F"I would like to assure motorists that
OL,7,Fwe are taking the reports seriously
OL,8,Fand have increased our patrols in the
OL,9,Fareas surrounding the affected
OL,10,Fsections of the A2 and M20.
OL,12,F"This includes the use of drones with
OL,13,Fthermal imaging cameras that are being
OL,14,Fused to monitor footpaths and wooded
OL,15,Fareas, and will allow officers to
OL,16,Frespond quickly to any suspicious
OL,17,Factivity.
OL,19,F"Volunteer officers from the Special
OL,20,FConstabulary have also been assisting
OL,21,Fus."
