OL,3,CPolice deploy drone cameras in hunt
OL,4,Cfor those who fired objects at drivers
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, Ashton Cull
OL,7,Ffrom the Road Haulage Association
OL,8,Fsaid: "We often don't see the real
OL,9,Fvictims in these incidents.
OL,11,F"You see a large vehicle, but you
OL,12,Falmost forget about the person inside
OL,13,Fit who's driving it, and not just that
OL,14,Findividual but the business owners who
OL,15,Fare put out of pocket when they have
OL,16,Fto repair these vehicles.
OL,18,F"A lot more needs to be done to tackle
OL,19,Finstances like this, and broader
OL,20,Ffreight crime and broader attacks on
OL,21,Fvehicles across the road network."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
