OL,3,CPolice deploy drone cameras in hunt
OL,4,Cfor those who fired objects at drivers
OL,6,FBen Lindley was one of those affected
OL,7,Fby the fired objects. He was driving
OL,8,Fhome on the M20 on Thursday night (7
OL,9,FNovember) when his windscreen was hit.
OL,11,FHe said: "All of a sudden I heard this
OL,12,Falmighty bang from the passenger side
OL,13,Fof the car.
OL,15,F"I had no idea what had happened, I
OL,16,Fslowed right down and was shaken."
OL,18,FHis windscreen had been struck by an
OL,19,Funknown object, causing it to crack.
OL,20,FShards of glass also fell onto his
OL,21,Fpassenger seat.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
